  "contentHtml": "In this episode Michael talks with guest Merill Fernando\n                  (\n                     <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://www.linkedin.com/in/merill/'><i class=\"fa-brands fa-linkedin\"></i></a>\n                     <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://twitter.com/merill'><i class=\"fa-brands fa-x-twitter\"></i></a>\n                  ) \n                  about the Zero Trust Workshop, but we also spend time talking about all things identity! Merill's final thought is pure gold.\n\n                  <br>\n                  The only Azure Security news item is about Azure SQL DB and TDE.\n\n                  <br><br>\n\n                  <!-- Insert episode info from rss.com into NNNNNN and TTTTTT which is the episode number and the title -->\n                  <iframe loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://player.rss.com/azsecpodcast/2297382?theme=light\" class=\"podcast-player\" title=\"The Azure Security Podcast\" frameborder=\"0\"><a href=\"https://rss.com/podcasts/azsecpodcast/2297382/\">MF2</a></iframe>\n\n                  <!-- Links to transcription and news articles -->\n                  <h5>Links</h5> \n                  <ul>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://rss.com/podcasts/azsecpodcast/2297382/#transcript'>Transcript <i class=\"fa-solid fa-book\"></i></a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://techcommunity.microsoft.com/blog/azuresqlblog/everything-you-need-to-know-about-tde-key-management-for-database-restore/4416564\">Everything you need to know about TDE key management for database restore</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://microsoft.github.io/zerotrustassessment/\">Microsoft Zero Trust Workshop</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://merill.net/\">Merill's Blog</a></li>\n                     <l